{"tid":1536244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我諗大家有個concept要改一改，唔想再晚晚有手足被捕","createTime":"2019-09-03T15:10:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T15:24:45.000Z","uid":211270,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"64fa891836fcde407650d4009b47a5639c9d8f94","tid":1536244,"uid":211270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:10:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好多人仲以為自己乜都冇做 ，冇犯法就唔驚d狗，有狗埋黎都仲唔走，繼續鬧。</span></span><br />\n我想講 <span style=\"font-size: large;\">班狗而家就係擺明濫捕</span> ，鬧一句就撲低你<br />\n防暴畜龍一到就散真係咁難?<br />\n我都知你地好憎佢地，我都係<br />\n但係，<br />\n晚晚有手足比人拉，真係叫撚狗?<br />\n晚晚有手足係入面比狗打，係我地撚佢定佢撚返我地轉頭？<br />\n我唔係屌鳩同路人，但係我想改善下個行動模式。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我地散左 行兩步又可以返黎繼續撚</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">佢地上晒gear落地 人影都唔見個</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">肯定又攰又谷氣</span><br />\n<br />\n無謂在意一時之氣<br />\n全身而退，之後玩幾耐都得<br />\n<br />\n真係唔想再見到手足比人拉，仲要好多係真係無辜嘅 <br />\n<br />\n以後撚狗行動 一見到有狗出黎 真係快快手閃走 好唔好"},{"pid":"dbfed5c915f3133a0857d46448313dff4c820b8a","tid":1536244,"uid":257422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:10:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">(集中討論) 908 九月八日 2:00pm <br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館<br />\n《香港人權及民主法案》集會請願 ! ! <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">扯國旗!</span> <span style=\"color: blue;\">唱國歌 !</span></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536086\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536086</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/kCGOYms.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkCGOYms.jpg&h=ced74507&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/JGPEpwY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJGPEpwY.jpg&